GSD.product_version: versions from v4.2 to before v5.15.78
GSD.description:
btrfs: fix ulist leaks in error paths of qgroup self tests

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.15.78 by commit f46ea5fa3320dca4fe0c0926b49a5f14cb85de62, it was introduced in version v4.2 by commit 442244c9633292a147ab2b29e7007a7c8a3909b2. For more details please see the references link.
